Text: thank you so much for this collection. you made it easy to organize and you really do have damn near everything. lol. the only problem i found was on the track titled "Bolero" by Fancy... its actually plays satisfaction by rolling stones. but its ok... because i looked up the other song and its some crazy hardcore 80's track with a creepy music video and it was f**king hilarious. so totally worth it. thanks a bunch for this one. :)
